# Music Files

Store background music files in this directory.

## Recommended Setup

1. **File:** `graduation-piano.mp3`
2. **Format:** MP3 (best browser compatibility)
3. **Duration:** 2-5 minutes
4. **File size:** 2-5MB maximum
5. **Bitrate:** 128kbps (balances quality and file size)

## How to Add Music

1. Prepare your audio file as MP3
2. Place in `/assets/music/` folder
3. Update path in `/config/site-config.js`:
   ```javascript
   music: {
     musicPath: "assets/music/your-file.mp3",
   }
   ```
4. Test locally
5. Deploy to GitHub Pages

## Free Music Resources

- **Pixabay Music:** https://pixabay.com/music/ (Royalty-free)
- **FreePD:** https://freepd.com/ (Royalty-free)
- **YouTube Audio Library:** Studio.youtube.com (Google account)
- **Epidemic Sound:** https://www.epidemicsound.com/ (Subscription)

## Audio Formats

| Format | Compatibility | Size | Quality |
|--------|---------------|------|---------|
| MP3 | ✅ All browsers | Medium | Good |
| WAV | ⚠️ Large files | Large | Lossless |
| OGG | ⚠️ Limited | Medium | Good |
| M4A | ⚠️ Safari only | Medium | Good |

**Recommended:** MP3 format

## Compression Tips

```bash
# Using FFmpeg to compress
ffmpeg -i input.wav -b:a 128k output.mp3

# Or use online converter
# https://online-convert.com/
```

## Notes

- Music won't autoplay (browser policy requires user interaction)
- User must click the 🎵 button to start playback
- Pauses automatically when tab is hidden
- Volume set to 30% (user can adjust)
- Loops continuously when playing

## Testing

1. Open page locally
2. Click the music button (🎵)
3. Verify audio plays
4. Check volume level is reasonable
5. Test in different browsers

Enjoy! 🎵
